                                <p class="mb-0" style="color: var(--brand-primary); font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.85rem;">
                                    Async TcpClient implementation managing persistent socket connections across hundreds of local device IPs without thread-pool starvation.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="p-3 rounded-3 h-100" style="background: var(--bg-body); border: 1px solid var(--brand-primary);">
                                <h6 class="fw-bold mb-2" style="color: white; font-size: 0.9rem;">2. The Payload (JSON-RPC)</h6>
                                <p class="mb-0" style="color: var(--brand-primary); font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.85rem;">
                                    Custom byte-array serialization of raw JSON-RPC payloads injected directly into the firmware data stream.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="p-3 rounded-3 h-100" style="background: var(--bg-body); border: 1px solid var(--brand-primary);">
                                <h6 class="fw-bold mb-2" style="color: white; font-size: 0.9rem;">3. Data Normalization (Regex)</h6>
                                <p class="mb-0" style="color: var(--brand-primary); font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.85rem;">
                                    Utilizing compiled Regex engines to scrape and normalize critical metrics from non-standardized raw text returns.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

